tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE pro_shop_inventory (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  product_name VARCHAR(255),
  category VARCHAR(100),
  price DECIMAL(10, 2),
  inventory_count INT,
  last_stocked TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE sales_tracking (
    sale_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id INT REFERENCES pro_shop_inventory(product_id),
    sale_date DATE NOT NULL,
    quantity_sold INT NOT NULL,
    total_price DECIMAL NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE Sales (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    quantity INTEGER NOT NULL,
    price DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL,
    sale_date DATE NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE Restocking (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    supplier_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    quantity INTEGER NOT NULL,
    restock_date DATE NOT NULL
);
CREATE TABLE golf_course (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL, location VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL, course_length INT NOT NULL, number_of_holes INT NOT NULL)
CREATE TABLE product (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL, category VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL, price DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL, quantity_in_stock INT NOT NULL)
CREATE TABLE sales (id INT PRIMARY KEY, product_id INT NOT NULL, quantity_sold INT NOT NULL, sale_date DATE NOT NULL)
CREATE TABLE restocking (id INT PRIMARY KEY, product_id INT NOT NULL, quantity_restocked INT NOT NULL, restock_date DATE NOT NULL)
CREATE TABLE popular_products (id INT PRIMARY KEY, product_id INT NOT NULL, times_ordered INT NOT NULL)
